message.content:
Reinforcement Learning, Neural Networks, Rule Learning. 

Reinforcement Learning is the primary sub-category of AI in this paper, as the authors have implemented a reinforcement learning architecture as the reactive component of their control system for a simulated race car. They have also tested the tuning, decomposition, and coordination of low-level behaviors using reinforcement learning. 

Neural Networks are also present in the paper, as the authors used separate networks for each behavior in their control system. 

Rule Learning is also present, as the authors used a simple rule-based coordination mechanism in their control system.
